# 3) Why the web prompt should be native

## Decision

The web AI layer should be built natively in the Backfill dashboard.

It should not be delegated to Retell web chat.

## Reasoning

The native web app already owns:

* auth
* tenant context
* schedule page context
* coverage page context
* template and review surfaces
* publish preview and diff surfaces

The web AI layer needs tight integration with exactly those capabilities:

* preview cards
* before/after diffs
* schedule review panels
* clarification selection
* confirmation modals
* optimistic refreshes
* action history

Retell remains a strong fit for voice. It is not the right foundation for the in-app manager workspace.

## Conclusion

Use:

* Retell for voice
* Twilio for SMS
* native Backfill UI for web AI prompt

